{"tid":154852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【收租好過打劫】嘉湖長情收租業主 20年租金180萬","createTime":"2017-03-13T15:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T15:17:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e83d2b8b71a350399be54058b04549e70a409e57","tid":154852,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"本港息口未加，對收租客者未有影響，天水圍嘉湖山莊一位長情業主，收租20年估計收180萬元租，賺了樓價兼賺租。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產天水圍分區營業經理伍耀祖表示，嘉湖山莊麗湖居4座中層E室新近租出，單位實用面積446方呎，建築面積581平方呎，2房間隔，享內園及泳池景，月租9,700元，折合平均實用呎租21.7元。<br />\n伍耀祖指，業主於1996年1月以124萬元向發展商購入單位，之後一直將單位出租，今番租務回報高達9.4厘。業主收租長達20年，按月租收入平均價大約7,500元計，累計月租收入約180萬元，已超出當年購入成本，足證物業長線投資潛力相當優厚。<br />\n麗湖居4座低層E室面積相約，上月中註冊登記以399萬元售出，呎價8,946元，出租單位現市值逾400萬元，升值2.2倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161216/56055068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161216%2F56055068&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFATQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=db8af5c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161216%2F56055068&h=33897b54\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161216/56055068</a>"},{"pid":"531278fe1f4521f49c6f89dcf7ca6876adf58147","tid":154852,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"40年前買太古城 而家收一年租等於當年買入價添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1d1eef2a24cb49a2cae03c33ae26adadbce5f","tid":154852,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>40年前買太古城 而家收一年租等於當年買入價添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas